text: "Sunday Mornings" is a 1993 song by French singer-songwriter Vanessa Paradis and is the second single from her third studio album Vanessa Paradis. It went to number 49 in the United Kingdom, number 41 in France, number 51 in Germany and number 36 in the Netherlands. It was produced by Lenny Kravitz. == Track listing == ==References== Category:1993 songs Category:Pop songs Category:Vanessa Paradis songs
